about.summary: 'UpSet.js' is a re-implementation of 'UpSetR' to create interactive set visualizations for more than three sets. This is a 'htmlwidget' wrapper around the 'JavaScript' library 'UpSet.js'.
'UpSet.js' is a re-implementation of 'UpSetR' to create interactive set visualizations for more than three sets. This is a 'htmlwidget' wrapper around the 'JavaScript' library 'UpSet.js'.

name: r-upsetjs
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.9.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-upsetjs
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/upsetjs_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/upsetjs/upsetjs_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2fcea0d0fcaaf89c6d2cb2a9be03f63f5ea55eb00c58b43ce01e04240418de77

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-htmlwidgets
    - r-magrittr
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-htmlwidgets
    - r-magrittr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('upsetjs')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('upsetjs')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/upsetjs/upsetjs_r/
  license: AGPL-3.0-only
  summary: '''UpSet.js'' is a re-implementation of ''UpSetR'' to create interactive set visualizations
    for more than three sets. This is a ''htmlwidget'' wrapper around the ''JavaScript''
    library ''UpSet.js''.'
  license_family: AGPL
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/AGPL-3'
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
